---
title: Thai-Style Coconut Kidney Bean Curry with Lemongrass-Infused Fried Shallot Rice
description: It's hard to resist the subtle sweetness of this lush kidney bean dish. Bright lemongrass notes in the infused coconut rice gently accent the richness of coconut milk in this Thai-inspired curry dish.
